ogy and history he then served as a fulbright english teaching assistant living at an islamic boarding school in makassar indonesia upon returning to the us he turned his attention to the energy sector working for a residential energy efficiency startup in portland oregon before coming to stanford as an ips student at stanford he is learning how to influence policymakers to create economically and environmentally efficient incentives for growth in the renewable energy sector search people everything support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
